        "Answer": "(A) Julio is liable for special complex crime of robbery with rape since he raped the daughter of Antonio on occasion or by reason of robbery. Pedro, Pablito and Juan are liable for robbery by band. They cannot be held liable for robbery with rape because they had no participation in the rape committed by Julio. (B) They are liable for a special complex crime of robbery with homicide. The killing of the whole family was done by reason of the robbery. They are also liable for the rape of the three daughters as a separate crime, but it may be complexed with robbery with homicide if the rape was committed on the occasion of the robbery."
